---
// Cyprus Ceremony Styles
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-white" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:9yaent">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-32" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:uqvja8">
    <!-- Beachfront & Pier Ceremonies -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-24 items-center" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:uqvja7">
      <div class="order-2 md:order-1" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:uqvja6">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#FDF2F9] text-[#A81E82] text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded-full mb-6" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:c4z8ii">Ceremony Styles</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-secondary mb-6" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:q6yvqr">Beachfront & Pier Ceremonies</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:ceaeaf">
          There's something magical about saying "I do" with the sound of the waves in the background. Cyprus offers some of the most spectacular beachfront locations in Europe, from white sand beaches to private wooden piers stretching out into the turquoise sea.
        </p>
        <a href="/enquire2" class="inline-block text-[#A81E82] font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b-2 border-[#A81E82] pb-1 hover:text-accent-hover hover:border-accent-hover transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:ji8azk">
          Explore Beach Venues
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 md:order-2" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt0a">
        <div class="relative" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt09">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FDF2F9] rounded-3xl translate-x-4 translate-y-4 -z-10" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt08"></div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-stone-200" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt07">
            <img crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1695196265659-de691b30e7b7?auto=format&w=1200&q=80" alt="Cyprus Beach Wedding" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:x94nlr" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Rustic & Traditional -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-24 items-center" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt06">
      <div class="order-1" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt05">
        <div class="relative" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt04">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FDF2F9] rounded-3xl -translate-x-4 translate-y-4 -z-10" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt03"></div>
          <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-stone-200" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt02">
            <img crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1643856557143-09189e523fd6?auto=format&w=1200&q=80" alt="Rustic Cyprus Wedding" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:x94nlq" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="order-2" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:jblt01">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-[#F5F5F5] text-muted-foreground text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase rounded-full mb-6" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:c4z8ij">Tradition</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-secondary mb-6" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:q6yvqs">Rustic & Traditional Charm</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:ceaeag">
          Away from the coast, the Cypriot countryside is dotted with charming stone villages and traditional villas. These venues offer a more intimate, private experience with exceptional local food and a truly authentic Mediterranean atmosphere.
        </p>
        <a href="/enquire2" class="inline-block text-[#A81E82] font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase border-b-2 border-[#A81E82] pb-1 hover:text-accent-hover hover:border-accent-hover transition-colors" data-ps="src/components/destinations/cyprus/CyprusStyles.astro:ji8azl">
          Explore Rustic Venues
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
